properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Manasquan Inlet to Little Egg Inlet NJ out 20 nm; Coastal waters from Sandy Hook to Manasquan Inlet NJ out 20 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 11 at 3:33AM EST until February 12 at 6:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 3 to 5 feet expected.

* WHERE...The Atlantic coastal waters from Sandy Hook to Little
Egg Inlet, New Jersey.

* WHEN...From 6 PM this evening to 6 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO 6 AM EST WEDNESDAY
